'''Varmigio''' was a mineral that in trace amounts was used to make [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] cores operate. During the time of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], reports placed large concentrations of varmigio on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Karra]]. However, the reports were inaccurate, and the [[Mining/Legends|mining]] colony's underwriters, [[Mineral Assets Partnership]], withdrew support for the settlement.

